// SPDX-License-Identifier: PMPL-1.0-or-later
// Embedded Translation Data  all translatable strings for IDApTIK
//
// ~130 keys across 5 languages (en, es, fr, de, ja).
// Terminal commands, device type names, and technical terms stay in English.
// Only user-facing UI text is translated.
//
// Key naming convention: "section.subsection.item"
//   intro.welcome.title, intro.welcome.line1, ...
//   hud.alert.clear, hud.alert.noticed, ...
//   victory.title, victory.grade.s, ...
//   gameover.title, gameover.reason.security, ...
//   settings.title, settings.language, ...
//   worldmap.title, worldmap.subtitle, ...
//   ui.next, ui.skip, ui.start, ...

//  English (source language  all keys defined here) 

